sub_title: Software Engineering Manager at ACT Commodities
summary:
For the past 12 years I have led and implemented diverse kinds of web applications, while setting up production-ready projects from scratch. I have been able to work with companies around the globe and to travel across 30+ countries while having a lot of fun in the meantime.

I believe self-learning and adaptability are crucial in problem solving. I am always looking for more efficient ways of doing things. I enjoy learning new technologies and would describe myself as an ambitious and creative engineer.

I believe that a respectful attitude towards colleagues is fundamental for optimal performance in an organization.

As a musician I'm always up for a jam, also I love to discuss ideas, history and culture.
